5. THE LANDSCAPE — ZOOMED‑IN, HYPER‑DETAILED AIRSHIP DOCKS

The docks and their surroundings are a breathtaking, sky‑high tapestry of brass, canvas, wood, and the quiet, powerful presence of four legendary family members.

5.1 The Observation Balcony (Foreground – Grandfather Thomas’s Vigil)

The foreground is a wide, stone balcony extending from the passenger terminal, its floor pale grey stone polished smooth by countless footsteps. A brass railing — chest‑high, with ornate scrollwork — borders the edge. Below and beyond, the main landing zone stretches out, with airships and cranes. A few wooden benches are bolted to the stone, and a large, brass telescope on a tripod points toward the distant mountains.

Grandfather Thomas — The Guardian of Secrets (Tiny, Dignified Silhouette)

Standing at the railing, leaning on his Chronos‑Scepter, is Grandfather Thomas. His silhouette, though miniature, is rendered with exquisite, miniaturist precision:

